  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The OUTBACK180B features a powerful 180W white LED source with an impressive 191,301 lux output at 5m (1.8° beam angle) delivering exceptional brightness with a crisp 7,000K colour temperature. Versatile colour capabilities include dual colour wheels offering a wide spectrum with 14 colours plus open on the first wheel and 8 colours plus open on the second wheel. The dual gobo wheels (one fixed, one rotating) offer extensive pattern options with indexing and shaking functions for dynamic effects. Further effects include motorised focus, two prisms (24-facet circular and 5-facet linear) with overlap and indexing, and a frost filter. Control options include 3 and 5 pin DMX as well as optional wireless DMX capabilities, all housed in an IP65 rated enclosure.",
